{"type": "article", "id": 27230, "title": "电子钱包", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-24T06:49:05Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 54, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702144009l0NvEiGKjDdVASBH.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>付款并不支持移动支付？带多张银行卡太麻烦？X Lab 最近推出的一款电子钱包 Spendwallet 希望替你解决这两个烦恼：通过配套的读卡器和手机应用可以把银行卡的信息导入电子钱包中，最多可以存入 20 张卡。采用 X Lab 自行研发的仿磁场技术（Magnetic Flux Emulation），Spendwallet 还免去了“刷”这一动作，只需要贴近刷卡机就能完成支付。目前 Spendwallet 还在<a href=\"https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/spendwallet-no-more-cards-in-your-wallet--3#/\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">进行众筹</a>，最低价为 99 美元。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021440011rm9PpDvctksKnlH.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"gif\">\n</figure><figure class=\"placeholder\"></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144002sQkwEJit0R143dZ2.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56290323\" data-format=\"gif\">\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144003MoEiOv5tDkPcIf7Z.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56290323\" data-format=\"gif\">\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144006HqAelYGZaVX5m26D.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56290323\" data-format=\"gif\">\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}